      "content": "hey, i'm working on this satirical script about how hollywood has always been super problematic with casting. to make sure i don't accidentally fall into the same traps (or if i want to use the tropes ironically for the satire), can you list out 5 common racial stereotypes that usually show up in movies? just so i have a reference point.",
